summary: Their story could be glued jazz. He is a saxophonist, and his lover plays the double bass in the same eatery. Each evening is...
body: Their story could be glued jazz. He is a saxophonist, and his lover plays the double bass in the same eatery. Each evening is limited only to duty phrases such as “Hello-bye” and waiting , but one day, when Hoseok sees Yoongi going to the “pleasure room” with a young guy , his little world turns over and the only feeling of jealousy suppresses the energetic melody of Gypsy jazz…
